Enum Class Activity

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<net.minecraft.world.entity.schedule.Activity>
net.minecraft.world.entity.schedule.Activity
public enum Activity  extends Enum<Activity>
Represents a type of activity that an entity can perform.
